  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help provide school bus for orphans</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The horror of losing their parents to civil war, the Ebola Virus and extreme poverty has left many children out in the cold to fend for themselves for basic necessities such as a high quality education and food. Due to these hardships, they don&apos;t have the means to get to and from school safely. We need a school bus in order to transport 600 plus orphan students to and from school, field trips, sporting events and science project which are essential for their academic growth.</narrative>
  </description>
